OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright and
OL,6,Fsunny end to the day. Dry with thin
OL,7,Fhigh cloud overnight but staying dry
OL,8,Fwith light wind. Another warm night
OL,9,Ffor many, especially in urban areas
OL,10,Fand cities, while feeling slightly
OL,11,Fcooler in rural and coastal parts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAnother hot or very hot day
OL,14,Ffor most, with daytime temperatures
OL,15,Fwidely above average. Dry and
OL,16,Fpredominantly clear with some hazy
OL,17,Fsunshine in the morning. Wind
OL,18,Fremaining light for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
