OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FPredominantly staying bright and sunny
OL,7,Ffor most places, early morning low
OL,8,Fcloud affecting certain costal areas.
OL,9,FFeeling slightly cooler compared to
OL,10,Fprevious days but temperatures
OL,11,Fremaining above average.
